  <script>
    const sImg = document.getElementById('s')
    const mImg = document.getElementById('m')
    const lImg = document.getElementById('l')
    const xlImg = document.getElementById('xl')
    function setImgUrl() {
      const width = document.body.clientWidth
      const height = document.body.clientHeight
      if(width<=500){ // S
        sImg.style.display = 'block'
        mImg.style.display = 'none'
        lImg.style.display = 'none'
        xlImg.style.display = 'none'
      }else if(width>500 && width<=930){ 
        if(height > width) { 
          sImg.style.display = 'none'
          mImg.style.display = 'none'
          lImg.style.display = 'block'
          xlImg.style.display = 'none'
        }else {
          sImg.style.display = 'none'
          mImg.style.display = 'block'
          lImg.style.display = 'none'
          xlImg.style.display = 'none'
        }
      }else if(width> 930 && width<=1366){
        sImg.style.display = 'none'
        mImg.style.display = 'none'
        lImg.style.display = 'block'
        xlImg.style.display = 'none'
      }else{
        sImg.style.display = 'none'
        mImg.style.display = 'none'
        lImg.style.display = 'none'
        xlImg.style.display = 'block'
      }
    }
    setImgUrl()
    window.addEventListener('resize', setImgUrl);
  </script>
